title: Lebanese-born Sydney father Fouad Arja facing deportation for unlicensed driving, held in Villawood Detention Centre
text: A Lebanese-born Sydney father has spent 10 months in Villawood Detention Centre after being told he could be deported for driving without a licence. ...
